{{Quote|Your biscuits are splendid, as usual. Hard as wood, and most flavorful. I had forgotten how much I enjoy them. Human food gives no benefit to the incisors.|[[Ebrihim]] to [[Duchess/Legends|Duchess]] [[Marcha]]|<ref name="Assault at Selonia">''[[Assault at Selonia]]''</ref>}}
'''Hard-biscuits''' were common foodstuffs of the [[Drall/Legends|Drall]] and were frequently enjoyed by those of all classes.

Rich and flavorful, they were also overbaked in order to produce an incredible hardness that made them all but inedible to [[Human/Legends|Humans]]. Even for Drall they required diligent chewing to eat; they enjoyed the act of chewing the biscuits as much as the flavor itself.

